content:
Sure, here are the restated negative attribute versions of the questions:

1. I often lack the motivation to put in the effort required to perform at a high level.
2. I sometimes prioritize my personal interests over the team's goals.
3. I struggle to take initiative and be proactive in my work.
4. I tend to react to situations instead of being prepared and anticipating challenges.
5. I am not willing to put in extra effort to help my leader or team succeed.
6. I find it difficult to take ownership of my mistakes and failures.
7. I tend to make excuses instead of taking responsibility for my actions.
8. I am not confident in my ability to perform at a high level.
9. I struggle to communicate effectively with my team.
10. I am not always accountable for my commitments and follow through on my promises.
